  <!-- ==== GREYWRAP ==== -->
  <div id="greywrap">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4 callout">
        <div class="btn" style="background: url(img/ms-ico/14000161.png); background-size: contain; height: 100px; width: 100px;"></div>
        <h2>Bingo Book</h2>
        <p>Access our infamous Bingo Book! Guild members can earn points by destroying wanted players/rival guild members within our Bingo Book. 
          The top bounty hunter of the month will earn in game rewards!</p>
      </div>
      <!-- col-lg-4 -->

      <div class="col-lg-4 callout">
        <div class="btn" style="background: url(img/ms-ico/31000100.png); background-size: contain; height: 100px; width: 100px;"></div>
        <h2>Wishlist</h2>
        <p>Guild members may post Gears/Items they need. 
          It would be our responsibility as a guild to make sure our members are as highly geared as possible. 
          Have an item on the wishlist? Prioritize trading with other members first! 
          Need to sell an Item? Our Members might know a guy!</p>
      </div>
      <!-- col-lg-4 -->

      <div class="col-lg-4 callout">
        <div class="btn" style="background: url(img/ms-ico/trophy.png); background-size: contain; height: 100px; width: 100px;"></div>
        <h2>Trophies</h2>
        <p>Easily grind for trophies and other dailies with friends.
          We may also introduce guild-only trophies in the future!
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- col-lg-4 -->
    </div>
    <!-- row -->
  </div>
  <!-- greywrap -->

